{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a warm and elegant Contact Us page for AdHouse.in, an online jewellery brand. The tone should be friendly yet sophisticated, reflecting the beauty and trust associated with jewellery shopping.
    Hero/Welcome Section:
    Add a welcoming headline such as "We'd Love to Hear From You ✨" with a subtext like "Whether you have a question about our jewellery, need help with your order, or just want to say hello — we're always here for you."
    Contact Details Section:
    Display the following contact information with icons in a clean card or grid layout:
    
    📞 Phone: +91-XXXXXXXXXX (replace with your number)
    💬 WhatsApp: Chat with us on WhatsApp — "Tap to chat instantly!"
    📧 Email: support@adhouse.in
    🕐 Business Hours: Monday – Saturday, 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM IST
    📍 Address: (Add your city/state or warehouse address if applicable)
    
    Social Media Links Section:
    Add a heading like "Follow Us & Stay Inspired 💎" and include clickable icons for:
    
    Instagram – @adhouse.in
    Facebook – AdHouse Jewellery
    Pinterest – AdHouse.in
    YouTube – AdHouse Official (if applicable)
    
    Contact Form Section:
    Include a simple inquiry form with fields for: Name, Email, Phone Number, Order ID (optional), and Message — with a submit button labeled "Send Message 💌"
    Trust/Reassurance Line at Bottom:
    End with a short note like: "We typically respond within 24 hours. Your trust means everything to us — just like every piece of jewellery we craft."
    Design Notes:
    Use gold, ivory, or rose-gold tones to match a jewellery brand aesthetic. Keep the layout minimal, elegant, and mobile-friendly., Generate some hero section as well in top , Keep other things as well as it below form and contact detail 
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-contact-social-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: {{ block.settings.desktop_width_percent }}%;
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding }}px 20px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
  }

  .ai-contact-social-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-contact-social-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .ai-contact-social-subtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtext_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .ai-contact-social-icons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .ai-contact-social-link-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.icon_bg_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.icon_border_radius }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.icon_color }};
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-contact-social-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.icon_hover_bg }};
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .ai-contact-social-link-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: calc({{ block.settings.icon_size }}px * 0.5);
    height: calc({{ block.settings.icon_size }}px * 0.5);
    fill: currentColor;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-contact-social-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.heading_size }}px * 0.85);
    }

    .ai-contact-social-icons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      gap: 16px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<contact-social-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-contact-social-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-contact-social-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
      <h2 class="ai-contact-social-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.subtext != blank %}
      <div class="ai-contact-social-subtext-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subtext }}</div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ai-contact-social-icons-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.instagram_url != blank %}
